], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One problem\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every few minutes, the telecast would cut to slick cinematography of a masked, hooded individual-that's what the NBC broadcasters kept calling her, \\\"the Individual\\\"-sneaking the Olympic torch around.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.94320884439628e-13, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the telecast\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"cinematography\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"a masked, hooded individual\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic torch\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She went to the Louvre, where the paintings came to life.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2631, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9999959481301864, \"rank\": 4.051886011160458e-06, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the paintings\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She went to a movie screening, where a Lumi\\u00e8re-brothers film ... came to life.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a movie screening\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These segments hit with all the force of a cruise-ship commercial, while distracting from the novelty of having a ceremony on water in the first place.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These segments\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"all the force\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"a cruise-ship commercial\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"the novelty\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"a ceremony\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The live components of the show were not much more vibrant.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The live components\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A bridge was converted into a runway on which fashion models and drag queens strutted with the gusto and precision of a forced march.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A bridge\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2973}, {\"ngram\": \"a runway\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion models\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"the gusto\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"precision\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"a forced march\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Platforms over the river itself featured extreme-sports performers doing tricks that the TV cameras seemed suspiciously afraid of showing in close-up.\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Platforms\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme-sports performers\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"tricks\", \"from\": 